hopobject.body: I'm originally from Dublin but now live in Edinburgh dexatol27 for sale australia Home is now a flat in Crouch End, in north London, where she lives alone with the dogs. When Smith says she’s single, there’s no apparent ruefulness. Her most significant ex is the comedian James Corden, of whom she speaks kindly. ‘Whenever someone’s been a big part of your life, you never stop loving them. Even if two people aren’t right, if you’ve got on well you want the best for them.’ Their on-off two-year relationship ended in 2009.
